block content
  p Let's start with this image.
  p Same title. Same painting. Same subreddit. One gets!{' '}
    span.bold 300
    |!{' '}votes. The other gets!{' '}
    span.bold 70,000
    | .
  img(src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/harrydry/gdmarketing/rs1.jpg" alt="Passive voice").img__100
  p People love!{' '}
    span.italic REAL
    |!{' '}stuff. But it's rare.
  p Lifeless marketing is everywhere and we copy it without thinking.
  p So I thought I'd share some examples of real stuff. Because the revolution can't be Googled.
  //- p Let's look at some REAL stuff.
  //- h2.under 1) Taleb's social proof
