  h2.under 6) Twitter's ads
  p Contrast Facebook and Twitter's out-of-home advertising.
  p Agency slogans Vs real tweets from customers.
  p Your own customers' words feels realer than an agency line
  p Nothing realer than customers words on your own app.
  img(src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/harrydry/gdmarketing/rs7.png" alt="Passive voice").img__100
  h2.under To wrap up
  p I'll leave you with my!{' '}
    span.bold real marketing manifesto
    | :
  p.inwardSpeech Real people. Real words. Real customers. Anything else goes.
  p I spent yesterday applying it to my email popup.
